    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/66105890cf350a6b97ddda3ce6407e1b.avif?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 2024 true-crime podcast &quot;My Escape from the Slackjaw Killer&quot; took America by storm—with its unflinching interview of his only known surviving victim. Painstakingly recreated from testimony, crime scene photos, and FBI reports, this game puts you in Slackjaw's world and asks: Will you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Average playtime: 1 hour</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/548fcc504b1b6b762291d0713c86c97a.webp?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=30 /></span>Explore the world of a serial killer as his next victim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/9d11cdd5b0b26cfa0a5f9f54d37c64ba.poster.avif?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/9d11cdd5b0b26cfa0a5f9f54d37c64ba.webm?t=1759082849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/9d11cdd5b0b26cfa0a5f9f54d37c64ba.mp4?t=1759082849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/4be4e4e9bead2ff4090ad30845cfed3e.webp?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=30 /></span>Use your wits and resources to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/63ae35b6563838484d0d4552e3d18cc8.poster.avif?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/63ae35b6563838484d0d4552e3d18cc8.webm?t=1759082849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/63ae35b6563838484d0d4552e3d18cc8.mp4?t=1759082849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/9472dc05755c3530e99846360628916f.webp?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=30 /></span>Uncover the twisted secrets buried deep within his basement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/cf52842ca716713b2471eed7786dfbc0.poster.avif?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/cf52842ca716713b2471eed7786dfbc0.webm?t=1759082849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/cf52842ca716713b2471eed7786dfbc0.mp4?t=1759082849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/4d6709ae2a7510d4c42ab56f5fbfaef2.webp?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=30 /></span>Escape to survive. But be quiet, he's upstairs....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/f41d86cfa52109cc288b43a4c8d83de2.poster.avif?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/f41d86cfa52109cc288b43a4c8d83de2.webm?t=1759082849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/f41d86cfa52109cc288b43a4c8d83de2.mp4?t=1759082849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073900/extras/7e511c3e41316a8f4596e0758c1ae7c1.webp?t=1759082849\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape room gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hyper-realistic graphics powered by Unreal Engine 5 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haunting original soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xbox controller support </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete in a single play session</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Created by a solo developer</p></li></ul>",
